"typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"bad4ebf5-0102-ddf2-2727-54b7d86f3a03","name":"Note: Download from Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Parse CSV Contents\n\nParses the incoming CSV binary into JSON items.\n\nNext: Clean & Reshape Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"89dbabf7-2898-7722-f716-2216be86b7e2","name":"Note: Parse CSV Contents"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Clean & Reshape Rows\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming document records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Rows Pass Validation?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"018f741d-ee22-984a-1de3-7e4998246d85","name":"Note: Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows Pass Validation?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.documentId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Rows into Google Sheets · ②→ Quarantine Bad Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"769069ad-57b6-cea2-f20b-37e6b96e1c07","name":"Note: Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Quarantine Bad Rows\n\nnotion — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"202a7625-4d12-ea1a-0ebe-1cd34abec0e6","name":"Note: Quarantine Bad Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Rows into Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Repack as XLSX · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"9dc727c5-ea0b-f812-0366-06051034cac0","name":"Note: Load Rows into Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Repack as XLSX\n\nSerializes items to a XLSX binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"150cb3bf-63f3-3812-424e-22ef7d001cf7","name":"Note: Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Processed File (Google Drive)\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Serialize Run Output (CSV) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"af327c35-85a4-a803-5870-02cce1ab8992","name":"Note: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"ea045f8f-7d4e-b4e7-ef95-d4daff638594","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"82801704-f48c-0bfa-5f7d-2c2ca5254a3e","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"a9b08c6d-ce06-4742-fb82-df6db5893ea5","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"35ad39cd-37ca-3505-0039-a8b75449cb00","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"1a7fe7cd-9a43-8cc5-42e6-925ea614a1d2","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"161086ae-f84f-8843-ab5f-4068e8cd2e44","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per document (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"3927bf8c-c934-c6c9-b82d-207369c647d3","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"c7a22288-9148-aff2-eefd-cf32d3c3019a","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"68aff5ef-f5ac-d144-e9b9-18d019cc98ee","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"b2b6d5b7-d5f7-6b46-848e-6d6c513cfb23","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"ab482399-40f2-9e25-2828-e75c793e9ce6","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty fileName","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"0558fe89-c46c-d87c-7001-86410b3835e3","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty fileName\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Sort Documents Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"a04a92e3-cf8f-f1a1-55a0-e54dca6d261b","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty fileName"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Documents Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"ba8d0697-cd3c-f1a6-871a-4e505551ec24","name":"Note: Sort Documents Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"e0aa52f8-2523-cc8a-619e-d01d73a34d49","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 25 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"0ad7076d-6ba2-dfa2-85f6-0c4b5e9f688b","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"849c3046-991b-5636-bc63-c969a02c0a1f","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"4721115f-dbdc-4adb-42d3-c16684e09415","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"67810f94-638c-c2cf-341f-4b6c02c19aea","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"bdd7de18-d27d-7c7c-e6ad-45ae2ef9e01f","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,1540],"id":"b6da1d40-cf55-fe72-de79-59a48c379851","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,1540],"id":"b7460842-440b-525b-f53b-3bb0cd492e83","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,1540],"id":"92f20b27-69de-4623-180a-619695dc7aaa","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Create contracts with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Document Generation · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nCreate contracts with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive 24/7. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual summarization is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Download from Google Drive → Parse CSV Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Google Sheets → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to document generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating summarization in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"4fea2ce7-50cb-a41b-405a-4dec34ff621f","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"cc8b5d39-b8ee-8ab0-5dc4-498a51b9713a","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"2da04113-3609-5575-8144-bf6bef13aced","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"ad951213-0881-e538-9bd0-5babdec16fca","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your summarization process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"d0205b35-f7e5-2c92-5751-9a5817e64124","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Download from Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download from Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse CSV Contents","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Parse CSV Contents":{"main":[[{"node":"Clean & Reshape Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Clean & Reshape Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Rows Pass Validation?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Rows Pass Validation?":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Rows into Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Quarantine Bad Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Rows into Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Repack as XLSX","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Repack as XLSX":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Copy to Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty fileName","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty fileName":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Documents Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Documents Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Quarantine Bad Rows":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b091da5b-4456-4d9a-99b4-4b8c58de412a","id":"FDX03448"}